WEBVTT

00:06:58.440 --> 00:07:00.976
In Japan, toilets are computers

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.896
and there's even hackers who hack them.

00:07:02.920 --> 00:07:04.696
(Laughter)

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.936
And we go further

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:09.176
and I give them these little stickers
with an on/off button on them.

00:07:09.200 --> 00:07:12.816
And I tell the kids,
"Today you have this magic ability

00:07:12.840 --> 00:07:16.456
to make anything in this room
into a computer."

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.816
And again, the kids go,

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:20.736
"Sounds really hard,
I don't know the right answer for this."

00:07:20.760 --> 00:07:22.336
But I tell them, "Don't worry,

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:24.936
your parents don't know
the right answer, either.

00:07:24.960 --> 00:07:27.176
They've just started
to hear about this thing

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:29.416
called The Internet of Things.

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:31.416
But you kids,
you are going to be the ones